      "tldr": "This release includes several dependency updates and security upgrades, addressing vulnerabilities in packages like minimatch, tar, and others. A new environment variable, AI_SDK_ENABLED, allows enabling the ai-sdk. Several fixes address issues with Gemini/VertexAI API error detection, cache hit rate calculation, Vercel stream tool call handling, file path handling in JetBrains, and CLI assistant creation. Additionally, the release incorporates improvements to OIDC trusted publishing and updates documentation for running checks locally."
